coding.display: For persistent or recurrent symptoms: get in touch with a local service for a Non-Urgent Appointment

text.div: <content>For persistent or recurrent symptoms: get in touch with a local service for a Non-Urgent Appointment (Dx09)</content> <br/> <content>Selected service: CPCS: Pharmacy 1 Test Profile Positive Solutions</content> <br/>

<content>Pathway: Calling About Self</content> <br/> <content>A report of results or tests was the reason for the contact.</content> <br/> <content>Instructions given were: If symptoms don't improve, or go away and come back, get in touch with a local service for a non-urgent appointment User Comment: test</content> <br/> <content>Advice Given: Worsening</content> <br/>

<content>Before you go, I will just check whether I need to give you any further instructions or advice.</content> <br/> <content>If there are any new symptoms, or if the condition gets worse, changes or you have any other concerns, call us back.</content> <br/> <content> </content> <br/>
